Item.Review:
Pros: Amazing sound quality best ive ever heard

Cons: Durability

When I first got these I didnt know what to expect.... But thank god.... these were worth the money. The sound quality is the best i have ever heard. Although the bad thing is that only after like a month or 2 they broke. The headband at the top is made out of a material that is far to easy to break. ;_;
